data.description: Beautifully updated townhouse in popularly sought after Persimmon Hill.  Brand new high end flooring greets you upon entering and leads into an open living space. Home has also been upgraded with new granite countertops in the kitchen.  Upstairs you'll find double masters as both bedrooms have their own full bathroom. Experience living in Persimmon Hill where HOA covers all roofing and outdoor siding along with lawn care and maintenance AND water and sewer usage included. Townhouse backs up to a gorgeous large pond making it a perfect setting for gatherings or relaxing.
